summary:
I am the geek who loves to share. Whether it’s a hobby, science, technology, or something that I have yet to fully understand. I have a strong belief that being exposed to different perspectives is the key to gaining knowledge on those matters I don’t quite fully understand. Perspectives are welcome through a hearty discussing or a different approach to a solution. 
	I have dedicated my life to the pursuit of self-growth and helping those in my community that they are entitled to the same pursuit regardless of their social, economic, or cultural background.  I have made this pursuit as a teacher, student, community club leadership, and other opportunities that have come and gone through my life.
